revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yargers}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yarger'' is the 15201<sup>st</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1938 individuals.
